{
  "title": "The Integrity Equation:",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">The Integrity Equation: <br/>Balancing Incentives, Loyalty and Ethical Judgment</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Explore how incentive structures, loyalty demands, and regulatory standards shape ethical decision-making in insurance. Review conflicts of interest tied to compensation, product placement, and organizational pressure, while emphasizing documentation and disclosure practices that withstand scrutiny. Real-world dilemmas illustrate how bias forms, where legal exposure arises, and how professionals protect themselves and their clients. Gain practical frameworks for evaluating ethical risk, managing competing obligations, and reinforcing trust through consistent, well-documented, client-first decisions. </p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$79.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>180 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph